# REQUIREMENTS.md

This template is copied to `.planning/REQUIREMENTS.md` by `/gsd-new-paper`.

The role is the same as GSD's REQUIREMENTS.md: the place where decisions get pinned. Distinguishes LOCKED (committed) from OPEN (still under discussion or deferred to a future phase).

